{"tid":613953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三種搞笑方法，黃子華，杜汶澤，林敏驄","createTime":"2018-04-02T06:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T07:56:05.000Z","uid":27495,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c255e36b385f7d5ee4a6124ae81f0f7e08734d2b","tid":613953,"uid":27495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"黃子華：將生活上一啲普通人覺得正常嘅野於喺其他地方上/用返自己理解演繹，等你地覺得好笑。例如游泳四式放係跑步上，船到橋頭自然直唔通條船去到橋頭會直咩。<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤：主要係講啲有味笑話（你對波真係好大）賤野（我同盧覓雪可以話比大家聽世上係有男女之間嘅純友誼）同屌下人，佢搞笑方式要有個下把俾配合佢，等個下把講啲野佢可以再無限滑波落去。<br />\n<br />\n林敏驄：佢主要玩食字gag，包括係有味笑話（粉紅色雨雲，可遇不可求)同粗口諧音（含住粒欖講野）<br />\n<br />\n其實搞笑就係聯想力嘅彰顯，你本身係邊悶撚，你都唔洗止意學到。"},{"pid":"212ca6adc371ec65b543f75c406311aa12964594","tid":613953,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"捷捷呢"},{"pid":"e47933ecf02c912a5be2d2eabbfd8c4a7a2afa8b","tid":613953,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"212ca6adc371ec65b543f75c406311aa12964594","tid":613953,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"捷捷呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"呢個勁"},{"pid":"acc7f4da4683a7720430f1848053605d5d2d2a7b","tid":613953,"uid":27495,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>捷捷呢</blockquote>呢個勁</blockquote><br />\n邊撚個捷捷"},{"pid":"3288d9d4cf54bc351c356c57a32cc9f77bd2f797","tid":613953,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"周星馳？"},{"pid":"0d8757f18cf305214a40fba9a30828a23a9a368b","tid":613953,"uid":156511,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e47933ecf02c912a5be2d2eabbfd8c4a7a2afa8b","tid":613953,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"212ca6adc371ec65b543f75c406311aa12964594","tid":613953,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"捷捷呢"},"c